reviews.review_text: Great show Maybe others have reviewed another SBD of this show, but if not, I can't believe I am the first to do so. The setlist is decent, and the mix is good (not perfect - Bob's guitar seems too loud, Brent's mic too soft). But otherwise, how can this show be passed over, considering 8/17 and 8/19, i.e. the first and last shows of this legendary 3-night Greek Theatre run, get so much attention?
Show me something built to last... Phil's bass way up in the mix
